{
  "stem": "8916.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, that's-- something that's an incredible thing, I should say.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And for that, you know, there were many heroes in-- in this-- in this war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I would place my parents as in-- in that category as heroes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They genuinely did these things quietly and were-- and suffered and did whatever they did.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But not only was it thanks to Schindler that we survived, but it was thanks to my parents.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In May, in May-- May 8 or May 9, 1945.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in Brunnlitz, and the first--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- well, first of all, Schindler told us that the night before or the day before that the war is over and that-- that we were-- we were free.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No one moved, because we were stunned.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- we weren't-- it's not like-- it's not like the movies, where now we're free, and everybody just goes off into happy land all of a sudden.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were-- we were crippled people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after spending that much time being humiliated and-- and under Nazi occupation, we were just-- we just didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- we stayed in the camp for a few weeks until a transport was formed, and we were repatriated.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a program of repatriation of people who were moved from one country to another and wanted to return.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there was a train being formed that was going to Poland from-- from Brunnlitz, and we got on it because--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The whole-- all the Leysons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was the natural thing to do, to go back where we came from.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we got off the train, and people got off at different-- in different places closest to their home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we got off in Cracow, and we were well received by my father's friends from before the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
